About Me

Hello,

My name is Dallas Davis

Future Web Developer | Web Designer



I became fascinated with web development at a young age. I took a class where all the students created a simple web page from scratch using raw HTML and the notepad application. Since then I have always had an interest in the web development field. The way things are done and utilized are much different than in the past. But that is just one more thing I love about this industry. I enjoy design the most, but there are no aspects of the web development business that find insubstantial. I enjoy learning and growing and hope to become a well rounded developer in my future.
